Strategies Offered by Berens Capital Management, LLC
Berens Global Value
Global long-biased portfolio of equity managers with a focus towards emerging markets. Target high absolute returns over a full business cycle.
Berens Asia Ex-Japan
Asia long-biased equity portfolio that is positioned to capitalize on consumer growth in Asia. Target high absolute returns over a multi-year period.















